<section class="warm-band">
  <div class="container-shell grid gap-8 py-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.9fr] lg:items-center">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-5xl leading-tight text-neutral-950 md:text-6xl">A neighborhood dumpling kitchen with a bright yellow sign.</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-neutral-700">Juicy Dumplings is built around simple food done carefully: steamed dumplings, warm wonton soup, crisp sides, and quick service for families, students, and regulars in Doncaster East.</p>
      <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <%= link_to "Order Online", order_path, class: "btn-primary" %>
        <%= link_to "Book a Table", book_path, class: "btn-secondary" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border-4 border-white bg-white shadow-2xl">
      <%= image_tag "shop_front.jpg", alt: "#{business_setting.business_name} shop front", class: "h-[430px] w-full object-cover" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container-shell py-14">
  <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="section-card p-6">
      <p class="eyebrow">Fresh Daily</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl text-neutral-950">Small-batch comfort.</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-600">Dumplings and wontons are presented simply, with clean broths, generous fillings, and familiar sides.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="section-card p-6">
      <p class="eyebrow">Friendly Pace</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl text-neutral-950">Easy pickup and dine-in.</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-600">The site is built around the choices customers need most: menu, ordering, booking, hours, and contact details.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="section-card p-6">
      <p class="eyebrow">Local Focus</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl text-neutral-950">Made for Doncaster East.</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-600">Warm cream, soft yellow, and dark charcoal styling now reflect the real shop-front instead of a generic template.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
